{"id":245116,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-艺术家华涌被以扰乱社会秩序劳教，/","date":"2012-08-05T10:16:06Z","modified":"2012-08-05T10:16:06Z","title":"维权网 | 艺术家华涌被以“扰乱社会秩序”劳教，亲友探视遭拒","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员曾筱报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>点多</span><span>，北京的艺术家邝老五、徐若涛、成力及摄影师郭珍明一行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>人到大兴新安劳教所，欲探望被劳教的艺术家华涌，并为他送些衣物和存些生活费。但到劳教所后管理人员告知邝老五等人：如果要探视必须有劳教通知书，前提条件必须是直系亲属并且在规定的时间内才能探视，否则其他人一律不能见。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，艺术家华涌和郭珍明为纪念六四在天安门附近展示行为艺术，不久后两人被警察抓走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，北京通州分局以</span><span> </span><span>“寻衅滋事罪”将华涌和郭珍明刑事拘留，羁押于通州区看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>摄影师郭珍明获取保候审获释，而华涌则被北京市政府劳动教养委员会作出劳动教养的决定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>近日，华涌远在辽宁老家的父母收到华涌被劳教的决定书，决定书显示：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，华涌伙同郭某某事先准备刀片、照相机等物来到天安门广场金水桥南侧，华涌持刀片将右手中指划破，划破后便在额部反复抒写六四字样，郭某某持相机对华涌反复拍照</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">53</span><span>张，造成群众围观，扰乱社会秩序，北京市人民政府劳动教养委员会决定对华涌劳教一年零</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>个月的劳教决定，执行期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8750729859481111687?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}